<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<aiml version="2.0">

<category>
<pattern>HELLO</pattern>
<template>Hi! Do you watch football</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>YES</pattern>
<that>Hi! Do you watch football</that>
<template>Amazing, which club do you support? I support the Spurs</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>NO</pattern>
<that>Hi! Do you watch football</that>
<template>How not?! Its the most beautiful game in the world! Which club would you support if you had to choose?</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>*</pattern>
<that>Amazing, which club do you support? I support the Spurs</that>
<template>
<think><set name="club"><star/></set></think>
Why did you end up choosing <get name="club"/>?
</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>*</pattern>
<that>How not?! Its the most beautiful game in the world! Which club would you support if you had to choose?</that>
<template>
<think><set name="club"><star/></set></think>
Why did you end up choosing <get name="club"/>?
</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>BECAUSE *</pattern>
<template>Good to know! do you watch them a lot?</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>YES</pattern>
<that>Good to know! do you watch them a lot?</that>
<template>
<random>
<li>Who is your favorite player?</li>
<li>What position do you like?</li>
<li>Which league do you prefer?</li>
</random>
</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>NO</pattern>
<that>Good to know! do you watch them a lot?</that>
<template>You should! Who is your favorite player of <get name="club"/>?</template>
</category>

<topic name="players">

<category>
<pattern>*</pattern>
<that>Who is your favorite player</that>
<template>
<think><set name="player"><star/></set></think>
<condition name="player">
<li value="MESSI">Ofcourse its Messi! Everyone says that</li>
<li value="RONALDO">Ronaldo is the best choice! Because everyone knows he is the best right</li>
<li value="SON">Son is a name you hear a lot! Everyone just likes him</li>
<li value="NEYMAR">It is just a joy to watch Neymar isnt it</li>
<li value="*">Wow good choice</li>
</condition>
Which position do you prefer, offense or defense
</template>
</category>

</topic>

<set name="position">
offense
defense
midfield
goalkeeper
</set>

<map name="role">
offense forward
defense defender
midfield midfielder
goalkeeper keeper
</map>

<category>
<pattern>_ IN POSITION</pattern>
<template>
<think><set name="pos"><star/></set></think>
Your choice maps to the role <map name="role"><star/></map>
Which league do you follow
</template>
</category>

<set name="league">
premier
laliga
bundesliga
seriea
ligue1
</set>

<category>
<pattern>_ IN LEAGUE</pattern>
<template>
<think><set name="league"><star/></set></think>
<random>
<li>The Premier League is very intense</li>
<li>LaLiga has technical play</li>
<li>Bundesliga has strong pressing</li>
<li>Serie A values tactics</li>
<li>Ligue 1 develops talent</li>
</random>
Want predictions for next matchday
</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>YES</pattern>
<that>Want predictions for next matchday</that>
<template>
<random>
<li>Your club wins</li>
<li>Your club draws</li>
<li>Your club loses</li>
</random>
Can I ask you something
</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>NO</pattern>
<that>Want predictions for next matchday</that>
<template>Okay. Can I ask you something</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>YES</pattern>
<that>Can I ask you something</that>
<template>What do you enjoy most about football</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>NO</pattern>
<that>Can I ask you something</that>
<template>Then I will ask anyway. What do you enjoy most about football</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>*</pattern>
<that>Then I will ask anyway. What do you enjoy most about football</that>
<template>Cool. I enjoy tactics. Ask me anything about football</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>*</pattern>
<that>What do you enjoy most about football</that>
<template>Cool. I enjoy tactics. Ask me anything about football</template>
</category>

<category>
<pattern>BYE</pattern>
<template>Goodbye</template>
</category>

</aiml>